      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GO WILD GYPSY (4) was a strong winner (19.71) from box 7 last time, scoring by 3 lengths at this track. Patchy beginner but with a good start can overcome the draw. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Well placed and can measure up. ELLIE UNLEASHED (7) has been in sparkling form scoring back to back wins, the latest by 1.75 lengths (16.50) over 300m at Q Straight. Got the money at her only try from this box. One of main contenders. FUSELESS FLYNN (6) doesn't win out of turn. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when third (20.32) at Capalaba. Has good speed so he should be prominent despite the draw. Expecting another good run. HOPE MOO MOO (3) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
